
# ⚗️ ChemSpecAI — Chemistry Document Intelligence Platform

## Project Purpose & Problem Solved

**ChemSpecAI** is an enterprise-grade **RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) system** designed to:

1. **Accept PDF uploads at runtime** — Users upload SDS (Safety Data Sheet) or TDS (Technical Data Sheet) documents
2. **Automatically classify, chunk, and embed** — Process documents without pre-loading data
3. **Answer natural language questions** — Using agentic tool-calling retrieval grounded in uploaded documents

**Problem Solved:** Chemists, safety officers, and engineers need quick, accurate answers from chemistry documents. Manual searching through lengthy SDS/TDS PDFs is time-consuming. This system enables **semantic Q&A** over chemistry documents with source-grounded answers.

